vote.title: Authorize (1) the transfer of $572,000.00 from the Skillman Corridor TIF District Fund to the Transportation Special Projects Fund to implement a public street lighting improvement project in Tax Increment Financing Reinvestment Zone Number Fourteen (Skillman Corridor TIF District); (2) an increase in appropriations in an amount not to exceed $572,000.00 in the Transportation Special Projects Fund; and (3) the disbursement of funds in an amount not to exceed $572,000.00 from the Transportation Special Projects Fund - Not to exceed $572,000.00 - Financing: Skillman Corridor TIF District Fund
